{"tid":620465,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【咁補鑊？】亞航被揭亂扔行李 地勤咀行李 網民反應兩極","createTime":"2018-04-07T15:02:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-07T16:11:27.000Z","uid":29627,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2bde84bc5af04c65087e0b062b3da51f77bdc1a4","tid":620465,"uid":29627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T15:02:26.000Z","msg":"馬來西亞亞航（AirAsia）早前有乘客拍下地勤人員搬運托運行李時，隨便亂扔導致損毀的影片，令公司形象受損。有亞航的地勤人員為「補鑊」，發佈多張親吻行李箱的照片，向乘客道歉並承諾會好好處理托運的行李。<br />\n<br />\n有關照片最先在上月底於facebook傳開，並發文表示：「親愛的行李箱，不管你有多重，我們都會一樣好好愛你、照顧你，請原諒我們之前所犯的錯吧！」後來有不少同事模仿，分享工作時親吻乘客行李的照片，有人將行李整件抱起親吻，亦有人彎腰向行李箱送上情深一吻。<br />\n<br />\n網民反應兩極，有人說很可愛，不過更多人表示噁心又多餘，「用心坦誠工作就好，別動作多多」、「戲王之王」，也有網民笑言這些行為「比扔行李更可怕！現在必須消毒了！還是盡量別搭亞航&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180405/large/1522916846_3b85.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180405%2Flarge%2F1522916846_3b85.jpg&h=ebee7ad9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180405/large/1522916849_8fd8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180405%2Flarge%2F1522916849_8fd8.jpg&h=e9372f61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180405/large/1522916847_2a4e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180405%2Flarge%2F1522916847_2a4e.jpg&h=afd3c74d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180407/58035740\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180407%2F58035740&d=dLhXG9g0xhpmkhj2B4UuqRxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=e7c0772f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180407%2F58035740&h=c787b610\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180407/58035740</a>"},{"pid":"9565ad626308ead99083458736f8529ac5c34d5b","tid":620465,"uid":712,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T15:07:46.000Z","msg":"咀完再掉"},{"pid":"a4b246d2cf13b0f62d83c3447f61c4ee1ec9e7bf","tid":620465,"uid":176366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T15:27:16.000Z","msg":"想補鑊定搞大鑊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abaab37a687044709893f9f268ef3aae93bf5597","tid":620465,"uid":169468,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T15:32:40.000Z","msg":"屌，要咀都搵啲空姐咀啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"479ed531a9a7fb4168da793e3d7f960db6388a1b","tid":620465,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T15:50:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db2185d0bc08fd92fa0b564d98697fac5364f72e","tid":620465,"uid":18251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9565ad626308ead99083458736f8529ac5c34d5b","tid":620465,"uid":712,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T15:07:46.000Z","msg":"咀完再掉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T15:59:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"505b0ac474d2863c7a033fbf18658d96b1d5010b","tid":620465,"uid":24570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T16:03:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dfa86af5b727d938530c42a6658dfd996193e9d","tid":620465,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T16:04:04.000Z","msg":"樓上五毛多到"},{"pid":"a062537b2279e0e9babbc9853082c0cf5139de7f","tid":620465,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9565ad626308ead99083458736f8529ac5c34d5b","tid":620465,"uid":712,"like":5,